sequenceDiagram
	autonumber
	participant U as User Client
	participant FSDK as Firebase SDK
	participant FA as Firebase Auth
	participant API as Express API
	participant ADM as Firebase Admin SDK

	U->>FSDK: Login with Phone OTP
	FSDK->>FA: Verify OTP (HTTPS)
	FA-->>FSDK: idToken + refreshToken
	U->>API: REST request Authorization Bearer idToken
	API->>ADM: verifyIdToken(idToken)
	ADM->>FA: Validate signature and claims
	FA-->>ADM: uid + role claims
	ADM-->>API: decoded token
	API->>API: attach req.user and enforce RBAC
	API-->>U: 200/201 JSON response

